expression.expression-string: SELECT USER_LOGIN.ID AS ID, (SELECT USER_LOGIN.VALUE FROM USER_LOGIN WHERE CHANGE_TIME = (SELECT MAX(CHANGE_TIME) FROM USER_LOGIN WHERE ID = USER_LOGIN.ID GROUP BY USER_LOGIN.ID)) AS LOGIN, (SELECT USER_PASSWORD.VALUE FROM USER_PASSWORD WHERE CHANGE_TIME = (SELECT MAX(CHANGE_TIME) FROM USER_PASSWORD WHERE ID = USER_LOGIN.ID GROUP BY USER_LOGIN.ID)) AS PASSWORD, (SELECT USER_FULL_NAME.VALUE FROM USER_FULL_NAME WHERE CHANGE_TIME = (SELECT MAX(CHANGE_TIME) FROM USER_FULL_NAME WHERE ID = USER_LOGIN.ID GROUP BY USER_LOGIN.ID)) AS FULL_NAME, (SELECT USER_ROLE.VALUE FROM USER_ROLE WHERE CHANGE_TIME = (SELECT MAX(CHANGE_TIME) FROM USER_ROLE WHERE ID = USER_LOGIN.ID GROUP BY USER_LOGIN.ID)) AS ROLE FROM USER_LOGIN,USER_PASSWORD,USER_FULL_NAME,USER_ROLE WHERE USER_LOGIN.ID = USER_LOGIN.ID AND USER_LOGIN.ID = USER_PASSWORD.ID AND USER_LOGIN.ID = USER_FULL_NAME.ID AND USER_LOGIN.ID = USER_ROLE.ID GROUP BY USER_LOGIN.ID
